flowchart TB
    subgraph LEGEND[Legend]
        LU[Backend]
        LC[Client]
        LM[Provider MCP]
    end

    A["Browser Starts Compliance Run (User submits provider repositories and standard)"]
    B["Compliance API Request (POST /api/compliance/evaluate or /evaluate-standard)"]
    C["ComplianceController (Main orchestrator for controls and checks)"]
    D["Input Validation (Validates provider, repository, and standard)"]
    E["OAuthService (Loads stored tenant access token)"]
    F["Framework Controls (Loads control definitions for selected standard)"]
    G["Control-Check Resolver (Maps each control to check IDs)"]
    H["Checks Catalog (Loads check definitions from checks.json)"]
    I["Check Resolver (Finds check by check_id)"]
    J["Canonical Tool Selector (Reads canonical tool name from check)"]
    K["ToolExecutionStrategy (Executes mapped tool with execution preference)"]
    L["ToolResolver (Resolves execution mode and mapped tool names)"]
    M["Tool-Name Mapping (Maps canonical tool to mcpToolName and restToolName)"]
    N{"Mode Decision (Uses preference and MCP exposed tools)"}

    O["McpClient (Calls mapped mcpToolName via JSON-RPC tools/call)"]
    O1["Provider MCP (Executes MCP tool on GitHub/GitLab/Bitbucket MCP server)"]
    O2["MCP Response (Returns raw MCP evidence payload)"]

    P["RestToolFallbackClient (Calls mapped restToolName)"]
    P1["REST Tool Contract (Loads matching entry from rest-tool-contracts.json)"]
    P2["Request Builder (Builds method, path, query, and body from contract)"]
    P3["Provider REST API (Executes HTTP API request)"]
    P4["REST Response (Returns raw REST evidence payload)"]

    Q["ResponseNormalizer (Normalizes evidence payload shape)"]
    R["Evidence Collection (Collects normalized evidence per check with metadata)"]
    S["EvaluationEngine (Evaluates check logic and returns check verdict)"]
    T["Result Aggregator (Aggregates check verdicts into control PASS/FAIL/ERROR)"]
    U["ReportFormatter (Builds display-friendly report block)"]
    V["EvidenceReportCollector (Writes evidence report JSON and returns download link)"]
    W["API Response (Returns result JSON with evidence_report link)"]
    X["Client UI (Displays compliance results and report link)"]

    A --> B --> C --> D --> E --> F --> G --> H --> I --> J --> K --> L --> M --> N

    N -->|MCP| O --> O1 --> O2 --> Q
    N -->|REST| P --> P1 --> P2 --> P3 --> P4 --> Q

    Q --> R --> S --> T
    T --> U --> W --> X
    T --> V --> W

